TiO2/TiO2-x;
ZrO2/ZrO2-x;
HfO2/HfO2-x;
SrTiO2/SrTiO2-x;
GaN/GaN1-x;
CuCl/CuCl1-x; und
GaN/GaN:S.

The switch of claim 8 wherein the at least one material for the primary active region and the material for the secondary active region are selected from the following list:
TiO2/ TiO2-x;
